:5px\">(0.50)</span></span></li><li><span><a href=\"#/courses/view/65b870096cd589f3a9e901c1\" target=\"_blank\">ECE380</a> <!-- -->-<!-- --> <!-- -->Analog Control Systems<!-- --> <span style=\"margin-left:5px\">(0.50)</span></span></li><li><span><a href=\"#/courses/view/69a70b0ddf9c42c28b55bf40\" target=\"_blank\">ECE423</a> <!-- -->-<!-- --> <!-- -->Embedded Computer Systems<!-- --> <span style=\"margin-left:5px\">(0.50)</span></span></li><li><span><a href=\"#/courses/view/68fb7ec38bfd1492804a7518\" target=\"_blank\">ECE457C</a> <!-- -->-<!-- --> <!-- -->Reinforcement Learning<!-- --> <span style=\"margin-left:5px\">(0.50)</span></span></li><li><span><a href=\"#/courses/view/65b8752a6cd58998d9e901e4\" target=\"_blank\">ECE481</a> <!-- -->-<!-- --> <!-- -->Digital Control Systems<!-- --> <span style=\"margin-left:5px\">(0.50)</span></span></li><li><span><a href=\"#/courses/view/65b875b798f04407171031e1\" target=\"_blank\">ECE486</a> <!-- -->-<!-- --> <!-- -->Robot Dynamics and Control<!-- --> <span style=\"margin-left:5px\">(0.50)</span></span></li><li><span><a href=\"#/courses/view/65b8761b5c947972e1e56c07\" target=\"_blank\">ECE488</a> <!-- -->-<!-- --> <!-- -->Multivariable Control Systems<!-- --> <span style=\"margin-left:5px\">(0.50)</span></span></li><li><span><a href=\"#/courses/view/673df068ea44ee0c210f9f15\" target=\"_blank\">ECE495</a> <!-- -->-<!-- --> <!-- -->Autonomous Vehicles<!-- --> <span style=\"margin-left:5px\">(0.50)</span></span></li><li><span><a href=\"#/courses/view/65b944e318ca2318600b6f4d\" target=\"_blank\">MTE544</a> <!-- -->-<!-- --> <!-- -->Autonomous Mobile Robots<!-- --> <span style=\"margin-left:5px\">(0.50)</span></span></li><li><span><a href=\"#/courses/view/664cbb492ed76bc0a3d8dabb\" target=\"_blank\">SE380</a> <!-- -->-<!-- --> <!-- -->Introduction to Feedback Control<!-- --> <span style=\"margin-left:5px\">(0.50)</span></span></li><li><span><a href=\"#/courses/view/68c043380e3dbaf2af35b3a5\" target=\"_blank\">STAT341</a> <!-- --